l avstanden v\u00e6re enda st\u00f8rre. Dette fordi de fleste store kj\u00f8ret\u00f8y bruker lengre tid p\u00e5 \u00e5 bremse opp.", "\u2013 Disse kj\u00f8ret\u00f8yene f\u00e5r forenklet forelegg for en tidsavstand p\u00e5 mellom 1-1,5 sekund, og f\u00f8rerkortbeslag fra ett sekund og nedover."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "7f88739f404547d2ac3768a466643e813d299ad1c690ff4663fc5a98e6042dff"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2013-01-24T07:37:27.852Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "S\u00e5 enkelt unng\u00e5r du den vanligste \u00e5rsaken til trafikkulykker i S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6997815.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Biler2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/bf0112265e0382b6bd3d64c3b621a01dbf5cee47.jpg?59729726"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Hold avstand og tell til tre -adressa.no", "1001, 1002, 1003", "Kan miste f\u00f8rerkortet"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "bf0112265e0382b6bd3d64c3b621a01dbf5cee47"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["avstand", "politiet bruker", "forenklet forelegg", "sekund", "vanligste \u00e5rsaken", "kort avstand", "p\u00e5kj\u00f8rsel bakfra", "bilen foran"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": 